narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would say it is a difficult class but you can succeed in it.
I would not recommend this class- the course material moved so quickly there was not really time to learn it and the teachers were not really helpful.
In my opinion, a math class that's definitely for people who feel confident in their Calc 1 (AB Calc) abilities or have already taken Calc 2 (BC Calc).
